Directory structure
===
- album: to be used for all album, image handling
- static: to store css, js and all static content
- users: to be used for all user related features
- templates: to store all templates


Dev installation
===
1. Clone the project to your local
2. Duplicate web_album/settings_default.py to web_album/settings.py
	Don't delete web_album/settings_default.py
	The idea is to have your own settings on your local

3. Change DATABASES
4. Run command: python manage.py syncdb
5. Start server: python manage.py runserver


